Author’s Note: Oh man.  You guys are going to kill me, but I needed to write a fluff fic.  I’m sorry.  I love writing my drama, romance, and angst stories, but I needed something that was just for fun.  It’s not going to be a long story (probably only a few chapters) and it’s just for me, but if you guys like it too, then all the better.  BTW, I don’t know Gabe’s secretary’s name or if he even has one, so just pretend that I know what I’m talking about.  In case you’re not familiar with my writing –  “represent spoken words” and ‘represent thoughts’.<br>
