<br>
“You think you can handle it that long?”<br>
<br>
“Dad!”<br>
<br>
“Sorry honey,” Gabe said.  “But Lex is a young man, and I’m sure he doesn’t want to have a teenage girl’s thoughts in his head for longer than he has to.”  Chloe folded her arms across her chest.<br>
<br>
