<br>
“You’re right, I’m sorry,” he apologized.<br>
<br>
‘You don’t want my thoughts inside your head?’  Lex asked.<br>
<br>
‘No.  In fact, I’m going to look for my dad’s scotch as soon as you leave.’<br>
<br>
