<br>
Chloe walked up to the Kents’ front door and hesitated before ringing the bell.<br>
<br>
‘Ugh,’ she thought.<br>
<br>
‘What’s wrong?’<br>
<br>
‘I just got to Clark’s house,’ she explained.  ‘And I should be happy, but instead I’m kind of nervous.’  Chloe turned to look at her car.<br>
<br>
‘Feeling the overwhelming urge to run away?’  Lex asked.<br>
<br>
