<br>
‘He didn’t invite him?  How could he not invite him?’  She thought.<br>
<br>
‘Do you need me to come over?’<br>
<br>
‘Why?  To protect me from Clark?’  Chloe scoffed at the thought.  <br>
<br>
‘No, to help you study for history,’ Lex thought sarcastically.  Chloe held back on rolling her eyes and looked at Clark somewhat suspiciously.<br>
<br>
“Do you mind if I ask why?”  She asked.  Clark took a few steps and then sat down next to her on the couch.  It was a little closer than he normally sat, but Chloe didn’t think anything about it.<br>
<br>
“I wanted to have some time alone with you,” Clark admitted.  Chloe’s eyes grew wide.<br>
<br>
“W-what?”<br>
<br>
