<br>
“Yeah, he would pretty much freak out,” she agreed.  Clark nodded.<br>
<br>
“So, how are you feeling?”<br>
<br>
“I’m fine Clark.”<br>
<br>
“No, I mean, are there any other side effects?”<br>
<br>
‘Damn you Lex.  You got all my hopes up that Clark *might* actually like me and all he wanted to do was ask me more about the effects of the stupid chemical spill.’<br>
<br>
‘Really?’  Lex was surprised.  When Clark had tried to kiss Chloe, it didn’t look like a ‘just friends’ thing to him.<br>
<br>
