“Nope,” she said cheerfully.  Clark walked with her toward the door.<br>
<br>
“You could still stay,” he said hopefully.  Chloe laughed.<br>
<br>
“No offense, but as fun as studying for history *isn’t*, I think I’ll – mmph.”  Clark quickly pressed his mouth against hers, taking her completely by surprise.  <br>
<br>
‘Mmph?’  Lex asked.<br>
<br>
‘He’s kissing me.  He’s actually kissing me.’<br>
<br>
“What?!”<br>
